        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Highway Trust Fund Reform Act of 2019 </b></p> <p>This bill eliminates the requirement that all laborers and mechanics working on federal-aid highway and public transportation projects shall be paid wages at rates not less than the locally prevailing wage rate.</p>]]></text>
